# Pass-Vault Frontend ‚Äî Build Guide

> **For the teammate building the UI.** This guide pairs with the backend guide. You handle ALL encryption ‚Äî the backend never sees plaintext passwords or vault data.

---

## Tech Stack

- **Framework:** React (Vite)
- **Encryption:** CryptoJS (AES-256)
- **HTTP Client:** Axios
- **Routing:** React Router v6
- **State:** React Context + localStorage
- **Styling:** Your choice (Tailwind recommended)

---

## Step 1 ‚Äî Project Setup

```bash
npm create vite@latest pass-vault-frontend -- --template react
cd pass-vault-frontend
npm install axios cryptojs react-router-dom
```

### Folder structure to create:
```
src/
  api/
    axiosInstance.js
    auth.api.js
