## Data Flow Summary

```
Master Password (user input)
    ‚îÇ
    ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ‚Üí deriveMasterKey()  ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚Üí masterKey (in memory)
    ‚îÇ                               ‚îÇ
    ‚îÇ                        encryptData() / decryptData()
    ‚îÇ
    ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ‚Üí hashForServer()  ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚Üí masterPasswordHash  ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚Üí Backend (bcrypt hashes again)
```

---

## File Order to Write (Recommended)

1. `cryptoUtils.js` ‚Äî test in browser console first
2. `axiosInstance.js`
3. API modules (`auth.api.js`, `vault.api.js`, `utils.api.js`)
4. `AuthContext.jsx`
5. `Register.jsx` ‚Üí `Login.jsx`
6. `VaultEntry.jsx` ‚Üí `AddEntryModal.jsx` ‚Üí `StrengthMeter.jsx`
7. `Dashboard.jsx`
8. `App.jsx` routing + `PrivateRoute`
